<section id="fileformats">
  <title>xx.coord</title>

  <para>
    The <filename>xx.coord</filename> file contains the coordinates of
    all of the vertices in the finite-element mesh.
  </para>

  <figure>
    <title>Format of <filename>xx.coord</filename> files</title>
    <screen>
coord_unit = km     <lineannotation>Units of coordinates</lineannotation>
 1  0.000000e+00  0.000000e+00  0.000000e+00     <lineannotation>Vertex number, x, y, z</lineannotation>
 2  1.000000e+00  0.000000e+00  0.000000e+00
 3  0.000000e+00  2.000000e+00  0.000000e+00
 4  1.000000e+00  2.000000e+00  3.000000e+00
...
    </screen>
  </figure>

</section>
